<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">//before() /insertBefore(): м„ нғқн•ң мҡ”мҶҢмқҳ мң„(htmlкё°мӨҖ)м—җ мҡ”мҶҢ мғқм„ұ</span>
